title: ISSS626-GAA
text:
Introduction
Welcome to my journey through ISSS626 Geospatial Analytics. This website contains my coursework that were completed through this course.



About
My name is Arjun Singh and I am a student at Singapore Management University pursuing a Masters degree in Analytics. This website documents my journey of learning Geospatial Analytics under the guidance of Professor Tin Seong Kam.
If you have any inquiries, feel free to reach out to me at arjun.singh.2023@smu.edu.sg
